		        <h2 class="header">ABOUT US</h2>
		        <p class="grey-text text-darken-3 lighten-3">Online restaurant management led by women is a growing trend that emphasizes inclusivity and innovation in the culinary industry. Female entrepreneurs are increasingly taking the lead in creating and managing online platforms that showcase their culinary talents. These women often prioritize sustainability by sourcing local ingredients and implementing eco-friendly practices. They leverage social media to engage with customers, share recipes, and promote their unique dining experiences. Women-led online restaurants frequently focus on community building, fostering connections between diners and local suppliers. Additionally, they may offer diverse menu options that reflect cultural heritage and personal stories. The use of technology, such as mobile apps for ordering and delivery, streamlines operations and enhances customer convenience. Female leadership in this space encourages a more equitable industry, inspiring future generations of women in food and hospitality. Overall, the rise of online restaurant management by women is reshaping the dining landscape, making it more dynamic and accessible..</p>
